Package: dubois
Title: Collection of functions that render Du Bois based plots from custom datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ícaro Bernardes",
          family = "dos Santos Coutinho",
          email = "icaro@bitanalytics.dev.br",
          role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package is under development. One function is already available coupled with an example dataset. The function takes a dataset and other arguments and delivers a plot in image format.
